[About the creation of the map]

New year new month and a new day...01.01.2009

We deside to build a new and gooder virsion of the orginal css map aim_ak_colt

We only spend 2 h with building and mabe 30min with debugging and then the map workt fine

I have to go now... but i will write more here tomorrow...



[Feature]

 * realistic ground and stone walls
 * afternoon skybox ("hav")
 * some crates around the map (big ones)
 * deagle (around spawn) and machine guns (two in the air)'
 * two bridges that conect two of the blocks ( hope you understand that :P)
 * rotating credits in the midle
 * and alot more...

[aboute the machine guns]

if you are skilled at jumping are you able to jump from the bridge and grab one xD 
I just wanted to make a small skillpuzzle :P



We hope you have fun wile playing this new version of the classic CSS map aim_ak-colt

[this map was made by me M4A1|a12 killingspree and my friend M4A1|Ninja Cheaton]
